    <td><h3>Tell Me</h3>
    <p>Students enrolled in a therapeutic support program in New York were concerned about bullying, and wanted to do something to prevent it. Along with their teachers, they came up with the idea of creating a video that would share their stories and empower others. The theme of the video is &ldquo;Tell Me&rdquo; – as in tell a teacher, parent, administrator, or coach when you are being bullied or witness bullying. The creators of the video want all students to feel safe and supported in their school, and this video lets them know that they are not alone.</p>
    <p align="center"><iframe width="640" height="360" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/YAGgYnHHU28?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p></td>
